{{!
    @template local_openveo_api/settings_page

    OpenVeo API settings page template to configure communication with OpenVeo.

    Context variables required for this template:
    * title - The translated title of the page
    * form - The HTML of the formular
    * connectionmessage - The HTML of the notification message about connection test

    Example context (json):
    {
        "title": "Settings page title",
        "form": "<form>[...]</form>",
        "connectionmessage": "<div class='alert [...]'>[...]</div>"
    }
}}
<div class="local-openveo-api-settings-page">
    {{{connectionmessage}}}
    <h2>{{title}}</h2>
    {{{form}}}
</div>
